data.title: SyneRyder
data.meta_description: SyneRyder's personal website.  SyneRyder is a software developer, occasional songwriter and entrepreneur.
data.text: SyneRyder (aka Kohan Ikin) is a software developer, occasional songwriter & entrepreneur. Kohan is the founder of namesuppressed, a graphics & audio software business. His software has been published in magazines worldwide, his music was nominated in the 2003 WAMi Song Of The Year awards, and he has been interviewed on BBC World radio. SyneRyder is the creator of the Kenny Translator and a fan of Nirvana. Need even more details? Need to contact me?
